      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DENNIS KEEPING (7) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a nose win at Wentworth Park in a handy 29.63. Wide box to overcome but has a good record over this journey. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Great chance to get the job done again. MOTOR CITY SONNY (6) flew the lids from out wide with an impressive turn of foot, going on to clock 29.67 when a 4 length winner over 515m at Gosford last time. Bold showing expected again. TRACEY TARO (4) is a super honest type rarely out of the placings, including wins at her last two on end, the latest at this track (22.62). Rarely misses off this draw. Looks well placed here and has the ability. Go well. VALEDICTORIAN (2) bold run expected on best form.",
